Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with formal logic, specifically linear temporal logic (LTL) specifications. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper discusses automatic synthesis for robotic motion planning and control of autonomous systems. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper also discusses load distribution in power networks. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is relevant as the paper discusses scenarios from robotics. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is less likely but still possible as the paper proposes an algorithm for synthesizing implementations.
